            "title": "💥系统开发环境配置",
            "date_published": "2020-12-04T03:38:58.000Z",
            "content_html": "<!--\n * @Author: Weidows\n * @Date: 2020-12-04 11:38:58\n * @LastEditors: Weidows\n * @LastEditTime: 2022-02-07 01:05:13\n * @FilePath: \\Blog-private\\source\\_posts\\system\\system_variable.md\n * @Description:\n-->\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F\">深入环境变量</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#scoop\">Scoop</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#jdk\">JDK</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#maven\">Maven</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#git\">Git</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#python\">Python</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#nodejs\">Node.js</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Weidows/Images/img/divider.png\" alt=\"分割线\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"深入环境变量\">深入环境变量</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"../%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F\">🎇 深入解析 Window 环境变量.</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"Scoop\">Scoop</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>详见<a href=\"../../tools/Scoop\">🙌Windows 平台软件包管理器选择 -Scoop</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Weidows/Images/img/divider.png\" alt=\"分割线\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"JDK\">JDK</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>通过 Scoop 安装会自动设置</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>新建 <code>JAVA_HOME</code> 环境变量值</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>D:\\Game\\Demo\\AdoptOpenJDK\\</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Path 里面添加</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>%JAVA_HOME%\\bin</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>JDK 创建 jre: 进入 JDK 根目录管理员模式输入(正常 JDK 自带)</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>bin\\jlink.exe --module-path jmods --add-modules java.desktop --output jre</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Weidows/Images/img/divider.png\" alt=\"分割线\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"Maven\">Maven</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>内部修改耦合 <a href=\"../../tools/IDEA/Modification#maven\">🎉IDEA 魔改记录.</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>环境变量: 用 Scoop 安装不需要手动配置!</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>检查</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mvn -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>VScode 中设置:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight json\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;java.configuration.maven.globalSettings&quot;</span>: <span class=\"string\">&quot;D:/Game/Scoop/persist/maven/conf/settings.xml&quot;</span>,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>IDEA 中设置也需要覆盖</p>\n<img src=\"https://www.helloimg.com/images/2022/02/27/GVshlQ.png\" alt=\"20210325105220\" />\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Weidows/Images/img/divider.png\" alt=\"分割线\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"Git-2\">Git</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>用 Scoop 安装自带环境变量, 不用配置.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Weidows/Images/img/divider.png\" alt=\"分割线\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"Python-2\">Python</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>通过 Scoop 安装会自动设置</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>Path 中 +<figure class=\"highlight taggerscript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">D:<span class=\"symbol\">\\G</span>ame<span class=\"symbol\">\\S</span>coop<span class=\"symbol\">\\a</span>pps<span class=\"symbol\">\\p</span>ython</span><br><span class=\"line\">D:<span class=\"symbol\">\\G</span>ame<span class=\"symbol\">\\S</span>coop<span class=\"symbol\">\\a</span>pps<span class=\"symbol\">\\p</span>ython<span class=\"symbol\">\\S</span>cripts\\</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>建议通过 Anaconda 安装有关 Python 的所有编程环境.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"../../others/python/anaconda\">👍Anaconda-Python- 水漂浅探池深浅.</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Weidows/Images/img/divider.png\" alt=\"分割线\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"Node-js\">Node.js</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>详见<a href=\"../../Web/Node/node\">⬆ Node.js 环境配置 &amp;&amp; 使用</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<script type=\"text&#x2F;javascript\" src=\"https://unpkg.com/kity@2.0.4/dist/kity.min.js\"></script><script type=\"text&#x2F;javascript\" src=\"https://unpkg.com/kityminder-core@1.4.50/dist/kityminder.core.min.js\"></script><script defer=\"true\" type=\"text&#x2F;javascript\" src=\"https://unpkg.com/hexo-simple-mindmap@0.8.0/dist/mindmap.min.js\"></script><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text&#x2F;css\" href=\"https://unpkg.com/hexo-simple-mindmap@0.8.0/dist/mindmap.min.css\">",
            "tags": [
                "maven",
                "备忘录",
                "计算机系统",
